---
layout: base.njk
title: "Reservieren"
permalink: /reservieren/
---

<style>
  .res-page { padding: 4rem 2rem 5rem; }
  .res-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .res-intro { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }

  .res-embed-box {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(167,195,195,0.45);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 2.5rem;
    min-height: 280px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .embed-placeholder { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); }
  .embed-placeholder p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .embed-placeholder code { background: var(--cream); padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.78rem; }

  .contact-fallback {
    background: rgba(167,195,195,0.1);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(167,195,195,0.4);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .contact-fallback h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
  .contact-fallback p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }
  .contact-fallback a { color: var(--black); }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">Strandmuschel Rantum</span>
  <h1 class="section-title">Tisch reservieren</h1>
</div>

<div class="res-page">
  <div class="res-inner">
    <p class="res-intro">{{ site.reservation_intro }}</p>

    <div class="res-embed-box">
      {% if site.reservation_system_embed %}
        {{ site.reservation_system_embed | safe }}
      {% else %}
        <div class="embed-placeholder">
          <p>Buchungs-Widget erscheint hier.</p>
          <p>Embed-Code im CMS unter <code>Einstellungen → Reservierungs-Embed</code> eintragen.</p>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="contact-fallback">
      <h3>Lieber telefonisch?</h3>
      <p>
        Für spontane Besuche, Gruppen ab 10 Personen oder Fragen zu besonderen Anlässen
        erreicht ihr uns unter <a href="tel:04651271750"><strong>{{ site.phone }}</strong></a>
        oder per E-Mail an <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}"><strong>{{ site.email }}</strong></a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
